INSERT INTO invoices (
                    invoice_id,
                    title,
                    month,
                    year,
                    is_main,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at,
                    deleted_at
                    ) VALUES (
                        $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8
                    ) RETURNING
                        invoice_id,
                        title,
                        month,
                        year,
                        is_main,
                        created_at,
                        updated_at,
                        deleted_at
